title: Parents of slain activist Rachel Corrie to speak at Kirkbride Hall (University of Delaware)
text: ( Source : University of Delaware ) 8:10 a.m., Oct. 8, 2015--Students for Justice in Palestine at the University of Delaware will host Cindy and Craig Corrie of the Rachel Corrie Foundation for Peace and Justice at 6:30 p.m., Tuesday, Oct. 20,
